en_949183_0	The Yovun Puraya -2019 program will be held in Weerawila next month.
en_949183_1	The initial discussion in this regard was held at the Prime Minister’s office under the patronage of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe and Minister Sagala Ratnayake.
en_949183_2	Yovun Puraya program is a brainchild of Premier Ranil Wickremesinghe.
en_949183_3	This year’s program will be held at the Livestock Resources Development Board in Weerawila from the 27th to 31st of next month.
en_949183_4	The Yovun Puraya project aims to educate country’s youth on national reconciliation and co-existence.
en_949183_5	In addition a range of cultural and recreational activities has been organized.
en_949183_6	Chairman of the Youth Council, Eranda Weli-ange and heads of security forces were part of the discussion.
